be that an elf can be set free by picking up a piece of clothing that
was left there by someone with the specific intention of freeing an
elf.  It is also possible that all Hogwarts students are part of the
&quot;family&quot; that the Hogwarts elves are bound to servc and therefore have
the power to free them.

